        "en": "<bb>ImmUnity Horizons</bb> is a three-day forum wherecomputation meets immunology.<br /><br />From <bb>9 – 11 July 2025</bb> in Tehran, researchers,engineers, and designers unite to decode immune data and build thenext wave of tools.<br /><br />Keynotes, a 48-hour hackathon, and hands-on workshops drive rapidcollaboration.<br /><br />Join us and help recode the future of health.",
